race.description: Cheers To 60! Happy Birthday Darryn Pateman Mdn
race.comment: SAVIENNE (10) showed good improvement last start when straight out to 1800m, closing strongly from the back of the pack. Now out to 2100m looks a good move and she can go to another level again now. Chris Parnham takes the ride and she can shed the maiden tag. FARADIO (3) disappointed last time out but was building nicely prior to that. He was a late scratching last month with a slight issue which is the query, but his form prior stands right up. Looks well placed here and a forward showing is expected. YOU CAN CALL ME AL (1) jumps right out in trip for the first time after closing strongly over the mile. He may get back from the draw, but rising in trip looks a good move and he can finish off strongly. KODY'S BELLE (9) improved last time out when over 2019m at Bunbury and is a big chance to go one better here. DANEA ROCK (7) is a long-time maiden but hasn't been far away in recent efforts. Keep safe.
